psidev.psi.mi.filemakers.xmlMaker.structure
Class XsdTreeStructImpl

java.lang.Object
  java.util.Observable
      psidev.psi.mi.filemakers.xsd.AbstractXsdTreeStruct
          psidev.psi.mi.filemakers.xmlMaker.structure.XsdTreeStructImpl

public class XsdTreeStructImpl
extends AbstractXsdTreeStruct

This class overides the abstract class AbstractXslTreeStruct to provide a tree representation of a XML schema, with management of marshalling of several flat files to a xml file that respects the schema

Author:
Arnaud Ceol, University of Rome "Tor Vergata", Mint group, arnaud@cbm.bio.uniroma2.it

Returns:
